#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Handling"
msgstr "压缩文件处理"

#. Tag: primary
#: archives.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archives"
msgstr "压缩文件"

#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing Archives"
msgstr "浏览压缩文件"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"vfs\">Virtual file systems (VFS)</link> allows you to "
"browse archives as if it was a folder. Currently &krusader; supports the "
"following archives types: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, rpm, "
"tar, xz, zip, and 7-zip and supports the following passworded archives: arj, "
"ace, rar and zip. Passwords can be stored in <application>KWallet</"
"application>. Please note that the archive support first needs to be "
"properly <link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">configured</link> in "
"Konfigurator. To open the archive, use &Enter; key, (double-)click or the "
"&Right; key. &krusader; supports also <emphasis role=\"bold\">hidden "
"archives</emphasis>, these are renamed archives with a *wrong* extension, "
"&eg; <trademark class=\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark> uses zip "
"archives with the following extensions: <literal role=\"extension\">.odt</"
"literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.sxw</literal> and <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.odw</literal>. &Enter; will open the <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark> document and the &Right; key "
"will open the archive. Another example is J2EE, where the <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.jar</literal> extension means a zip archive. Since "
"&krusader; auto-detects the supported archive types, it will open with "
"&Right; key even if it has another &MIME; type. Please note that browsing "
"archives has a few limitations:"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">虚拟文件系统 (VFS) </link>允许您像浏览文件夹一样浏览存"
"档。目前 &krusader; 支持以下归档类型："
"ace,arj,bzip2,deb,gzip,iso,lha,rar,rpm,tar,xz,zip 和 7-zip 并支持以下加密归"
"档：arj,ace,rar 和 zip。密码可以存储在 <application>KWallet</application> "
"中。请注意，归档支持首先需要在 Konfigurator 中<link linkend=\"konfig-"
"archives\">配置好</link>。要打开归档，请使用 &Enter; 键，双击/单击或 &Right; "
"键。&krusader; 也支持 <emphasis role=\"bold\">隐藏的归档</emphasis>，它们是"
"用 “错误的” 扩展名重命名的归档，&eg; <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark> 用以下扩展名使用 zip 归档: "
"<literal role=\"extension\">. dt</literal>, <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.sxw</literal> 和 <literal role=\"extension\">.odw</"
"literal>。&Enter; 将打开 <trademark class=\"registered\">OpenOffice</"
"trademark> 文档，&Right; 键将打开归档。另一个例子是 J2EE，其中 <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.jar</literal> 名意味着一个归档文件。&krusader; 自动检测到"
"支持的归档类型，所以即使它有另外一个 &MIME; 类型，它也将使用 &Right; 键打开。"
"请注意浏览档案有一些限制："

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all functions are supported by all archive types. (&ie;: you can not "
"delete files in ace or rar archives)"
msgstr ""
"并非所有归档类型都支持所有功能。 (&ie;: 您无法删除 ace 或rar 归档中的文件) "

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The permissions you have inside the archive are the same as the permissions "
"you have for the archive."
msgstr "您在归档中拥有的权限与您对归档拥有的权限相同。"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command line (if visible) will not follow you inside the archive but "
"will point to the archive folder."
msgstr "在归档文件中命令行 (如果可见的话) 不会跟着您，而是会指向归档文件夹。"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before any action is performed on files/folders inside the archive, they "
"must be extracted. The archive will be repacked when you leave it or when "
"&krusader; detects that extracted files have changed."
msgstr ""
"在对归档中的文件/文件夹执行任何操作之前，必须提取它们。 当您离开时或者当 "
"&krusader; 检测到提取的文件已经改变时，归档将被重新解压。"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Packing and un-packing are <quote>blocking operations</quote> that display a "
"progress dialog. However, this might change in the future since we are "
"planning to create more background operations."
msgstr ""
"打包和解压缩是显示进度对话框的 <quote>阻塞操作</quote>。然而，这种情况以后可"
"能会发生变化，因为我们正在计划开始更多的后台操作。"

#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unpack Files"
msgstr "解压缩文件"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are 2 ways to extract files from archives:"
msgstr "从归档中提取文件有两种方式："

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to unpack a whole archive(s), browse to the archive location, "
"select the archive(s) and select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Unpack</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo>. &krusader; will "
"ask you where to put the extracted files. The default location is the "
"inactive panel folder. If you do not cancel the operation, &krusader; will "
"try to unpack all the selected files in the inactive panel."
msgstr ""
"如果您想要解压缩整个归档，请浏览到归档位置，选择归档，然后选择 <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>文件</guimenu> <guimenuitem>解压缩</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> 或者 "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo>。"
"&krusader; 将询问您提取文件到哪里。默认位置是非活动面板文件夹。如果您不取消操"
"作， &krusader; 将尝试解压非活动面板中所有选中的文件。"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you only want to extract a part of the archive, then <link "
"linkend=\"browsing-archives\">browse</link> the archive and copy the files "
"you want to extract to their new location just as you would copy "
"<quote>normal</quote> files. Note that unpacking from a browsed archive "
"takes more time (file by file unpack) compared to unpacking a whole archive "
"with the first method. The unpack operation can be put in a <link "
"linkend=\"queue\">queue</link>."
msgstr ""
"如果您想要解压归档的一部分，请 <link linkend=\"browsing-archives\">浏览</"
"link> 归档文件并像您复制<quote>普通</quote>文件那样将您要解压缩的文件复制到"
"它 (们) 的新位置。注意与用第一种方法解压缩整个文件相比，从浏览过的归档解压缩"
"较慢 (一个一个地解压缩) 。解压缩操作可被放入<link linkend=\"queue\">队列</"
"link>。"

#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packing Files"
msgstr "打包文件"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to create a new archive, begin by selecting the elements you "
"want to pack in the active panel and select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pack...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>. A dialog will "
"pop-up prompting you to select the archive name and location. Select the "
"packer from one of the <link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">supported file name "
"extensions</link>."
msgstr ""
"如果您要创建一个新归档，请先选择活动面板中您要打包的项目并选择<menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>文件</guimenu> <guimenuitem>打包...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>或 "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>。一个对"
"话框将提示您选择归档文件名和它的位置。请从<link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">"
"支持的文件扩展名</link>中选择打包器。"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add files to an existing archive(s), open the archive in one panel and "
"the files to be copied in the other panel, then simply copy the files into "
"the archive in exactly the same way you copy files into a <quote>normal</"
"quote> folder. The pack operation can be put in a <link "
"linkend=\"queue\">queue</link>."
msgstr ""
"要向已有的归档文件添加文件，请在一个面板中打开归档并在另一个面板中打开要添加"
"的文件，然后像复制<quote>普通</quote>文件到文件夹那样直接把文件复制到归档文件"
"里。打包操作可被放入<link linkend=\"queue\">队列</link>。"

#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Testing Archives"
msgstr "测试归档文件"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; will not handle corrupted archives since it may result in data "
"loss. If you receive an error message when opening an archive, or if you "
"suspect that there is something wrong with the archive, you should test it "
"before use. To test an archive, browse (navigate) to the archive location "
"and select the archive. Next select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Test Archive</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>. &krusader; will test "
"the archive file and inform you whether the archive passed or failed the "
"file integrity test."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; 将不处理损坏的存档，因为这可能导致数据丢失。 如果您在打开归档时收"
"到报错消息，或者如果您怀疑存档有错误，您应该在使用前测试它。要测试归档，请到"
"归档所在的位置并选择归档，然后选择<menuchoice><guimenu>文件</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>测试归档</guimenuitem></menuchoice> 或 <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>。&krusader; 将测试归档文"
"件并告知您归档是否通过文件完整性测试。"
